Params: {2: 'Lee', 3: 'The abnormal signal should be coming from this area. The increase in bionics should indicate that we are approaching the core.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Stay alert. Keep an eye on the status of your M.I.N.D. at all times.', 3: '7'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "...It's best not to think too much about things in the bionics' Virtual M.I.N.D.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Don't put any extra burden on the commandant. Clear the remaining Amberia data in this area ASAP to end the battle.", 4: '1'}
